data.meta_description: Stuntman Super Dave Osborne disastrously performs unique stunts.
data.text:
EPISODE 1

Ultimate Slam Dunk

Fuji helps Super Dave perform the 'Ultimate Slam Dunk' using a hydraulic catapult that will raise him upright and shoot him into the air where he will catch the ball and slam dunk it.

23 min Â· Jul 4, 2022 PG

EPISODE 2

Lip Synching Concert Area

Super Dave originally plans to play 'Vehicle Tag' with Fuji, but instead shows off the new Outdoor Lip-Synching Concert Area.

23 min Â· Dec 5, 2022 PG

EPISODE 3

Vehicle Safety Centre - Buckle Up

At the Super Dave Vehicle Safety Centre, Super Dave acts as a crash test dummy and drives into a wall to demonstrate the dangers of not buckling up.

23 min Â· Dec 5, 2022 PG

EPISODE 4

Super Ride Straight To Hell

At the Heavy Metal Motorcycle Preparation Area, Super Dave attempts the 'Super Ride Straight to Hell' in which he will jump a three inch wide ramp and land on another three inch wide ramp across the field.

23 min Â· Nov 8, 1988 PG
